{"tid":56762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［腳膠］想問巾幗播左謝雪心露腳趾未？","createTime":"2016-12-27T13:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T14:29:06.000Z","uid":24050,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4eb147ddef35f3c056fd4ef77f88489a547db369","tid":56762,"uid":24050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:12:06.000Z","msg":"配合《巾幗》重口味 謝雪心獻出螢幕第一次<br />\n<br />\n拍畢三年的《巾幗梟雄之諜血長天》，盛傳因為有過多強姦、暴力甚至雞姦的重口味場面，所以一直被雪藏，出街無期。不過日前劇集終於解禁，明天(10月1日) 正式在myTV SUPER首播！劇中除了祥仔被雞姦、杏兒多次被強姦外，原來飾演乳娘的謝雪心亦作出好大犧牲，為大家獻出螢幕第一次！<br />\n<br />\n宣傳片其中一幕就見識到祥仔個日本商人角色有幾變態！畫面見到心姐唔知係瞓着咗還是被弄暈，然後祥仔笑得勁變態咁拎住剪刀，剪刀緩緩伸向心姐啲腳趾度&hellip; 大家都知佢想做咩啦！祥仔就勁陰森咁話︰「我要全世界嘅人都知道，咩叫做痛苦！」真係睇見都覺得痛！<br />\n<br />\n劇中除了杏兒破禁演出，有多次被強姦的場合，其實心姐都作出好大犧牲！從上文提及的戲份可見，心姐似乎會被祥仔剪斷腳趾，而呢次亦係心姐從影多年來第一次露出腳部，佢坦言拍攝時非常緊張！雖然佢都有要求導演唔露腳，不過因為劇情需要，最後都為大家獻出第一次！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdN1EAfVvkCKchvXwbYGcwGbMg2YSbben7hf32W5Q81cU?filename=KUF50Mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUF50Mx.jpg&h=f162e5a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcRaRGjVza54UQCDk4LfACjHPMn7AsckxEqX2bA4B6qw3?filename=32SiNiL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32SiNiL.jpg&h=8bd17adc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/210810_1519992969810211ea018438a8851d80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F210810_1519992969810211ea018438a8851d80.jpg&h=2c16a4f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n心姐咁大犧牲 <br />\n好想請定年假留係屋企坐定睇完打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴打知道幾時播<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99be2b76f53d536ab4ff310bc54bb06c4db6fc1e","tid":56762,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:12:34.000Z","msg":"我上網睇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0693fa9e60977e8aa319795ff01cb5e2ef5e6d","tid":56762,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:15:32.000Z","msg":"由尋日開始就唔訓等睇呢場戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2773abcbff50f7d6263caa84d0aa176e02136298","tid":56762,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:17:00.000Z","msg":"心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a5d39668480a6e29630338663e5e819574cfb5","tid":56762,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"好想奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ab6ae60c9ae59a138debe77544460fbc0a7873","tid":56762,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n推到腦魔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c728ab5bd4b23c9d339eb96a8dde541c7bd03